OL,5, The energy crisis is pushing more      
OL,6, households onto prepayment gas and     
OL,7, electricity meters, research suggests. 
OL,9,FComparison website Uswitch said 60,000 
OL,10,Fnew meters were installed in Britain in
OL,11,Fthe six months to March, reversing a   
OL,12,Flong-term trend of the number falling. 
OL,14,FIt says prepayment customers are more  
OL,15,Flikely to be vulnerable and at risk of 
OL,16,Fbeing, in effect, disconnected when    
OL,17,Fthey cannot afford to top up.          
OL,19,FMinisters promised to focus energy     
OL,20,Fsupport on the most vulnerable in 2023.
